properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 7 at 10:51AM MST until January 7 at 2:00PM MST by NWS Riverton WY
properties.description:
...High winds expected through 2 PM this afternoon from South Pass
to Jeffrey City to Casper...

* WHAT...Southwest winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 to 65 mph.

* WHERE...Green Mountains and Rattlesnake Range including Beaver
Rim and Jeffrey City.

* WHEN...Until 2 PM MST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile
vehicles. This includes travel along highways 287 and 220.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The strongest winds are expected before 12
noon this afternoon.
properties.instruction:
People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around
trees and branches. Use caution if you must drive.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 2 PM MST THIS AFTERNOON
